items.title: New Reports Call UnitedHealth’s Earnings Momentum Into Question. How Should You Play UNH Stock Here?
items.description: UnitedHealth stock sinks further on reports it quietly sold stakes in business units to preserve its streak of beating earnings estimates. Wolfe continues to recommend owning UNH shares here.

items.title: Stocks to Watch Wednesday: J&J, Bank of America, UnitedHealth, Goldman
items.description: ↗️ Johnson & Johnson (JNJ): J&J boosted its annual outlook, after posting better-than-expected quarterly profit and sales. Shares rose nearly 2% in premarket trading. ↗️ Goldman Sachs (GS): The Wall Street bank reported a stronger-than-expected quarterly profit, fueled by a pickup in dealmaking and surging trading during tariff-driven market turmoil.
